     <body>
     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="11"/>
   <head>To my loving Friend, The <hi>Author.</hi>
   </head>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <hi>
            <seg rend="decorInit">H</seg>Omer</hi> eterniz'd is for writing what</l>
      <l>
         <hi>Achilles</hi> and his <hi>Myrmidons</hi> did at</l>
      <l>The Siege of <hi>Troy.</hi> I envie not his fame,</l>
      <l>But needs must future <hi>Ages</hi> greatly blame,</l>
      <l>If they forget to Memorise thee too,</l>
      <l>That show'st not what was done, but how to doo.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>Rowland Gwyn.</signed>
   </closer>
